felix as a girl's name is pronounced feel-iks. it is of latin origin, and the importance of felix is "happy, happy". male felicity. the name of the roman dictator sulla. the names of the three popes and many saints. connected in the united states with the character of felix the cat (lat. feles, felis), and felix unger of "the odd couple". the american physicist felix bloch.,happy,happy, and prosperous, happy
